## Security & Isolation

### Sandboxed Execution
- Each agent runs in isolated Docker container
- No access to host system or other containers
- Controlled resource allocation and monitoring
- Secure handling of credentials and sensitive data

### Data Privacy
- User data remains within the container during execution
- Configurable data retention policies
- Secure transmission of results
- No persistent storage of sensitive information

## Performance Characteristics

### Scalability
- Horizontal scaling through container orchestration
- Parallel execution of multiple agent tasks
- Resource optimization for different task types
- Load balancing across available resources

### Reliability
- Error handling and recovery mechanisms
- Timeout protection for long-running tasks
- Graceful degradation when services unavailable
- Comprehensive logging and monitoring

